Name: Average time from \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ to \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average resolution time of \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ until \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ is performed again
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ to \Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER\ in cases where re-submission leads to approval
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum time it takes for a \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ to be followed by \Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR\
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ and the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all instances of \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ within a single case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Time until \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ from \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time between \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ and \Request Payment\ in cases that proceed to payment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time it takes from \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Total time from \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ to \Payment Handled\ in successful cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ to the next \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum resolution time of \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ in cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ to \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases where administration approval follows pre-approver rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
